<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-purple);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Commercial Fit-out</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Refurbishment</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Commercial refurbishment across London and the South East — strip-out, remodelling and M&amp;E upgrades to repurpose existing space. Much of it phased around live, occupied buildings, with the M&amp;E held in-house so the floor keeps running while we bring it up to standard.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Refurbishment →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Refurbishment,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Scope</span></h4><ul><li>Soft strip-out &amp; enabling works</li><li>Remodelling &amp; reconfiguration of existing space</li><li>M&amp;E upgrades &amp; services replacement</li><li>Occupied &amp; phased, out-of-hours works</li><li>Landlord re-lets &amp; space repurposing</li><li>Protection to base build on live floors</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Standards &amp; compliance</span></h4><ul><li>CDM 2015 across every package</li><li>Building Regulations — Part B and Part L on upgrade</li><li>CAR 2012 — asbestos awareness &amp; duty to manage</li><li>BS 8000 — workmanship on building sites</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you refurbish an occupied building without shutting it down?</summary><p>Yes. Much of our refurbishment work is phased around live, occupied buildings — soft strip and noisy works out-of-hours, floor-by-floor sequencing and tight protection to base build — so the building keeps running while we refurbish it.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>How do you handle asbestos in older buildings?</summary><p>We work to CAR 2012 and the duty to manage. Where a refurbishment or demolition survey flags asbestos-containing materials, licensed removal is arranged before our works proceed — strip-out doesn't start on assumptions about what's behind the wall.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you cover M&amp;E upgrades as part of a refurbishment?</summary><p>Yes, and it's the same contractor. We self-deliver M&amp;E upgrades — services replacement, lighting, power and public health — alongside the fabric works, so the refurbishment is coordinated under one accountable team rather than split across trades.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Part of Commercial Fit-out</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Explore the full<br>package.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><a class="sector" href="/commercial/">Commercial Fit-out overview</a><a class="sector" href="/commercial/cat-a/">Category A Fit-out</a><a class="sector" href="/commercial/cat-b/">Category B Fit-out</a><a class="sector" href="/commercial/integrated-me/">Integrated M&amp;E</a></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">The other three lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service lines.</h2></div><div class="otherlines reveal in"><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Commercial</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Fabric</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Groundworks</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div></div></section></div><section class="band" data-nav-dark="true" style="background: var(--m-green); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Talk to us about MEPH</div><h2 class="dhead sm" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Scope, programme,<br>stage — send it over.</h2><p class="body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); margin-top: 16px;">A named contact, not a sales team, comes back within 24 hours. Include the package, programme and stage if you can.</p></div><div class="cta-row2" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start;"><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">Enquire about MEPH →</a><a class="btn ghost" href="/compliance/">Compliance &amp; BSA</a></div></div></div></section></div><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList", "itemListElement": [{"@type": "ListItem", "position": 